        "created_at": "2022-04-17T16:08:14.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>we focus on Comtes de Champagne yet there\u2019s another interesting wine that a search finds very little about:  Folies de la Marquetterie. Made from the Pinot and Chardonnay vines around the estate, I can find only one mention on wb, by Brad in passing. I was at Taittinger recently and the wine wasn\u2019t shown or mentioned; of course, I forgot to ask. I bought a couple b from a recent Sokolin offering. Will check it out.</p>\n<p>Any info?</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.taittinger.com/de/folies-de-la-marquetterie\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/3/3/333e892dc3bb1c31f240e5351cd142829a00fc54.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.taittinger.com/de/folies-de-la-marquetterie\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">taittinger.com</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <img class=\"thumbnail\">\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.taittinger.com/de/folies-de-la-marquetterie\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Folies de la Marquetterie | Champagne Taittinger</a></h3>\n\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
